'''马修·阿布德'''（{{lang-en|Matthew Abood}}，{{bd|1986年|6月28日||}}）生于悉尼，是一名澳大利亚男子游泳运动员，主攻自由泳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.swimming.org.au/article.php?group_id=7299|title=Matthew Abood|work=Swimming Australia|accessdate=2020-07-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319155141/http://www.swimming.org.au/article.php?group_id=7299|archivedate=2015-03-19}}</ref>。2012年，他在全国游泳锦标赛50米自由泳项目上获得第三名，以0.02秒的差距无缘[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会|伦敦奥运]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.smh.com.au/sport/swimming/unlucky-matt-abood-finally-gets-his-commonwealth-games-chance-in-glasgow-20140716-zthqb.html|title=Unlucky Matt Abood finally gets his Commonwealth Games chance in Glasgow|publisher=[[悉尼先驱晨报|Sydney Morning Herald]]|date=2014-07-16|accessdate=2020-07-10|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200710085337/https://www.smh.com.au/sport/swimming/unlucky-matt-abood-finally-gets-his-commonwealth-games-chance-in-glasgow-20140716-zthqb.html|archivedate=2020-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年，他通过全国锦标赛获得男子50米自由泳和男子4×100米自由泳接力的奥运资格，得以首次参加奥运，在该届奥运中，他获得男子4×100米自由泳接力的铜牌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympics.com.au/olympians/matthew-abood/|title=Matthew Abood|work=[[澳大利亚奥林匹克委员会|Australian Olympic Comittee]]|accessdate=2020-07-10|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200710084704/https://www.olympics.com.au/olympians/matthew-abood/|archivedate=2020-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年7月，已经退役的阿布德开始在[[Optus|Optus]]工作<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.optus.com.au/about/careers/inside-optus/stories/from-olympian-to-optus|title=From Olympian to Optus - Getting to know Matt Abood|work=Optus|date=2018-11-22|accessdate=2020-07-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303155342/https://www.optus.com.au/about/careers/inside-optus/stories/from-olympian-to-optus|archivedate=2020-03-03}}</ref>。

